# 🏥 Healthcare AI Agent — Blood Glucose Monitor

A multi-agent AI healthcare assistant built with CrewAI that analyzes 
real patient blood glucose data and generates complete health reports 
with recommendations.

Built at a hackathon by a 3-member team, each owning a separate part 
of the codebase.

---

## 🤖 What It Does

- Loads a real clinical dataset of **16,969 patient records** from Kaggle
- Picks a random patient (or filter by age)
- **Agent 1** fetches the patient's full health record
- **Agent 2** analyzes all metrics and generates a health report
- Final report includes glucose classification, blood pressure, 
  heart rate, SPO2, symptoms, 5 health tips, and doctor advice

