- **Kaggle Dataset** — 16,969 real patient blood glucose records
- **Pandas + OpenPyXL** — data loading and processing
- **Python 3.10+**

---

## 📊 Dataset

**Dataset:** [Blood Glucose Level Readings](https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/ashmitcajla/dataset-for-blood-glucose-level-readings)

Contains 16,969 patient records with:
- Blood Glucose Level (mg/dL)
- Blood Pressure (Systolic/Diastolic)
- Heart Rate (bpm)
- Body Temperature (°F)
- SPO2 / Oxygen Level (%)
- Sweating and Shivering symptoms
- Diabetic / Non-Diabetic status

