## ⚙️ Setup & Installation

**1. Clone the repo**
```bash
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/healthcare-ai-agent.git
cd healthcare-ai-agent
```

**2. Install dependencies**
```bash
pip install crewai kagglehub pandas openpyxl groq
```

**3. Get a free Groq API key**

Sign up at [console.groq.com](https://console.groq.com) — free, 
no credit card needed.

**4. Add your API key**

Open `member_a_data.py` and replace:
```python
os.environ["GROQ_API_KEY"] = "gsk_your_key_here"
```

**5. Run the project**
```bash
python3 member_c_runner.py
```

